@page "/"
@attribute [Authorize]
<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">Hello, world!</MudText>
<MudText Class="mb-8">Welcome to your new app, powered by MudBlazor and Linger.Blazor components!</MudText>

<MudAlert Severity="Severity.Normal">
    You can find documentation and examples on MudBlazor website here:
    <MudLink Href="https://mudblazor.com" Target="_blank" Typo="Typo.body2" Color="Color.Primary">
        <b>www.mudblazor.com</b>
    </MudLink>
</MudAlert>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">Linger.Blazor 组件库</MudText>
<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
    Linger.Blazor 是一个基于 MudBlazor 的组件库，提供了以下功能：<br />
    <br />
    - 用户认证和令牌刷新<br />
    - 布局组件<br />
    - 数据展示组件<br />
    - 主题切换<br />
    - 全屏模式<br />
    <br />
    这些组件可以在任何 Blazor 应用程序中使用，无论是 WebAssembly、Server 还是嵌入到 WinForms/WPF 中的 Blazor。
</MudText>

<br />
<MudText Typo="Typo.h5" GutterBottom="true">组件示例</MudText>
<br />

<MudGrid>
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="4">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardHeader>
                <CardHeaderContent>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">网格单元格列表</MudText>
                </CardHeaderContent>
            </MudCardHeader>
            <MudCardContent>
                <MudText>用于展示网格化的数据，支持自定义颜色、选择和模板</MudText>
            </MudCardContent>
            <MudCardActions>
                <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary" Href="/grid-cell-demo">查看示例</MudButton>
            </MudCardActions>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
    
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="6" md="4">
        <MudCard>
            <MudCardHeader>
                <CardHeaderContent>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">用户信息</MudText>
                </CardHeaderContent>
            </MudCardHeader>
            <MudCardContent>
                <MudText>展示用户的详细信息</MudText>
            </MudCardContent>
            <MudCardActions>
                <MudButton Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Primary" Href="/profile/1">查看示例</MudButton>
            </MudCardActions>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
</MudGrid>